@231 = ~Burning Weapon~
@232 = ~Burning Weapon (Evocation)
Level: 3
Sphere: combat, elemental (fire)
Range: touch
Duration: 3 rounds + 1 round/level
Casting Time: 4
Area of Effect: touched weapon
Saving Throw: none

When he casts this spell, the preacher must touch a weapon. It then ignites by a magical fire that does not affect the wearer but adds 2D4 fire damage points when the weapon hits. The magic fire is added if the weapon is already a fire weapon, and does not turn into a magical weapon one that isn't already. It is possible to cast the spell on a creature, in which case its natural weapons burn. If the spell is casted on a missile weapon, the fire affects the projectiles, but they receive only 1D6 additional fire damage.~
