@233 = ~Fire Shield (Red)~
@234 = ~Fire Shield (Red) (Evocation, Alteration)
Level: 3
Sphere: protection, elemental (fire)
Range: 0
Duration: 3 rounds + 1 round/level
Casting Time: 4
Area of Effect: the caster
Saving Throw: none

The red fireshield protects the user from fire damage by surrounding the caster with a shield of flame. This shield not only grants the user 50% fire resistance, but also protects the caster from attacks made within a 1.5m radius around the caster. An opponent that hits the caster with any weapons or spells within this radius suffers 1d6 +2 fire damage.~
