@2310 = ~Exaltation (Abjuration) //Version IWDEE
Level: 3
Sphere: Healing
Range: Touch
Duration: 1 turn
Casting Time: 9
Area of Effect: 1 creature
Saving Throw: none

This spell enables a priest to aid and protect any one being other than the priest. By touch, the caster protec the recipient against the effects of fear, sleep, feeblemindedness, unconsciousness, and intoxication, as well as berserk and confused states of mind for the duration of the spell.
The preacher, having lost all healing skills, can't negate those effects on someone already affected.~

@2311 = ~Melf's Minute Meteors~
@2312 = ~Melf's Minute Meteors (Evocation, Alteration)
Level: 3
Sphere: elemental (fire)
Range: 0
Duration: special
Casting Time: 4
Area of Effect: the caster
Saving Throw: none

This spell enables the preacher of flames to cast small globes of fire (one for each experience level attained), each of which bursts into a 30-cm-diameter sphere upon impact, inflicting 1d4 +3 points of damage to the creature struck. It can also ignite combustible materials (even solid planks). The meteors are treated as missiles hurled by the preacherd with a +3 bonus to the attack rolls and with no penalty for range. Each meteor inflicts +3 damage, and an additional +3 fire damage.
The preacher may discharge up to four missiles per round.~
